    <tags>cli agent hub validation skill management</tags>
    <summary>CLI for agent hub validation, index generation, and skill management</summary>
    <description>
agentctl is a command-line tool for validating agent hubs, generating index files, and managing skills. 
It supports hub validation, index generation, skill installation/management, and configuration management.
    </description>
